{"tid":1291421,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於見到今朝突然多咗D光復Post","createTime":"2019-07-07T01:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T01:21:40.000Z","uid":274749,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"465fb12943a36732e191a164170afa06403fb094","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:03:29.000Z","msg":"純粹個人睇法<br />\n<br />\n我頗肯定而家係政府入面嗰D所謂*高手*，都會同阿7講「唔回應，就係最好嘅回應」。<br />\n<br />\n點解？因為佢哋可以，冇人可以迫到佢哋，除咗中央。<br />\n<br />\n我估佢哋其實就想我哋集中堅持5大訴求，因為佢知道禁樣遲早可以拖死我哋，D人會因為冇回應而慢慢流失。<br />\n<br />\n唔係建議唔講5大訴求，但係應該要更think out of the box，例如光復係香港嚟講真係小有嘅普世價值(藍/黃)，嚟緊區議會多一認同就有機多一張票。<br />\n<br />\n最後希望可以分享自己睇法，我覺而家阿7同某D高官最怕係乜？<br />\n<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n<br />\n觀乎阿7過往講嘅嘢，佢話過有佢一日係度，都唔會有哩樣嘢，真係好少見。<br />\n<br />\n各位，試諗下如果我哋攞返區議會同立法局，到時要成立獨立調查委員會就唔係冇可能。"},{"pid":"b1fa8ff656ddb5ce1645a9e6a36d4a927d49eb1c","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:05:21.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fc97a758288aede7152111fdcf58ae0be5725019","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:06:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7dbfd43d9f22f495fdde1989585c2cdcaa043bb4","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:07:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"45a9dc7889d7edbefeb34c68ede50802d7c53166","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:09:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e642c1b8f9a8bf29b0f70874f58f29d721f4e8b3","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb40538fd29b5865cb9ee86643180ea5a7c0d77f","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:13:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f073271b3d0b51f9f540ac85bb3c3cae3c1f1108","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:14:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"63e64faa216f67e27e9c40efd27cd6841eafd564","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:16:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"81af5e940f62705b2392902d2cfcb7bbec41fc4e","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:20:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b0015b91ff834feb15eb11981c596164fdb05db","tid":1291421,"uid":274749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T01:21:40.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}